This paper deals with natural language processing and machine learning techniques to predict the quality of paths in a knowledge graph. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also involves the use of neural networks, which falls under the sub-categories cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also deals with information retrieval and semantic similarity, which could fall under cs.IR (Information Retrieval) and cs.SI (Social and Information Networks).
